ne by the attackers within seconds.","weakness":{"id":27,"name":"Improper Authentication - Generic"},"original_report_id":null,"original_report_url":null,"attachments":[{"id":772758,"file_name":"bandicam_2020-04-04_07-06-41-299.mp4","expiring_url":"https://hackerone-us-west-2-production-attachments.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/vNk3AKS3nFanRrVeP9bjXN63?response-content-disposition=attachment%3B%20filename%3D%22bandicam_2020-04-04_07-06-41-299.mp4%22%3B%20filename%2A%3DUTF-8%27%27bandicam_2020-04-04_07-06-41-299.mp4\u0026response-content-type=video%2Fmp4\u0026X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256\u0026X-Amz-Credential=ASIAQGK6FURQYJPM5INV%2F20260429%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request\u0026X-Amz-Date=20260429T085335Z\u0026X-Amz-Expires=3600\u0026X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjECgaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJGMEQCIGPTFP%2F%2B61NRXKxUCRRiOEw%2FyEXMoJI30jSWgewoYzlYAiATW70r0%2Ft4BCmx%2BIRRvI9N9Vm6tq25cJqmqyf8P9oJnSq6BQjx%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F8BEAMaDDAxMzYxOTI3NDg0OSIMlnlVa%2Fn%2F5%2FBwcq%2BdKo4F1YnOHtgpcuOI6MB5pFrZ1JRxajUzrmu66Bs%2BaH059f9y01fPv%2FrjUZqEro3Jo9934IhhUwQj4gQeQ52XFU4tL%2Fl7ANAcg%2BweyQf%2FlO3JCodLg6QOdgOquP7BbCsXjast8Pomf8KP1lmk7IIMD7J9DS4cjH6SQasi3CttqywzFCaRrB8cbzZNYwGpMcshlGieMrYvXOKXlnFS%2Bvyupk%2BdoPGms%2F3cgeV%2BcDw50A71YHut794drWOwB%2BEgOIDnJqc%2FodmOUDjNrGX2PYH98D58CQI6kF0KLfi9CZmpJrhPYWDkdXTTag4OHihpyrvYSsSmxgEN1mpxlQWp3qqjt9qoTl0ks45f5BDGWqJfXqS6BToA%2FyYcov9sqsrq4OPo9luLGlSC2n3bSDp7b0kZjA1KI8sleyE39CFdrHoEX%2B7oWvUWQgHphH3Q8BMmkSeejy70EmY5sY8nHxzxh7Dad05tIOqTFbZ%2BZgtuZT5FDbkFzkwFhf31nqsw52N8uaKjg5OC9zTWIMWPyYbEsjRy8ysfEI7wOyEgz4hKw42ZE%2BQwchRJVzjIfG%2FydQmIL81YK37dK7j5m3h3w8krlkcHtnFLeC%2FQmM%2BeodTy4V71S6ERtrAKr2ItxzM%2FteX%2B0%2FWpQeoI%2FChXa3DA%2FggHvAyucAKgMnjSUwBn57W9JZy%2BJSPzMSBw7F7UxXSoITzG6M%2BYz%2Bl09U6QBtVUdjQuAZplrNQ0IupzAaYZmnJHy4JHrTrLDgyzizvbVD9nG7AAnJurFmdE1TbZ%2BGJuAN5Y0bsF0mLXDzkgZR7DysR0C1rvYL3m0Br4yjjflY40H7Oziol2n3YJxG1BOJ32K08Mn6Q3qE3VPzBHy7cpax6QTG2O20NZMJfyxs8GOrIBgtkoQeR9CK7lzLU7BrdeJifAyJIAHqtmKXqt4cHHZ2HzHdGeVq6r%2FyVIf9ImLQDdXY